                            <comment id="13561956" author="mbertozzi" created="Thu, 24 Jan 2013 20:30:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 HBaseAdmin is supposed to be synchronous and we don&apos;t have a way to catch when a modifyTable() operation is completed.&lt;/p&gt;

